|               |                                   HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(ss_sold_date_sk@1, d_date_sk@0)], projection=[c_customer_sk@0, ss_ext_sales_price@2, d_month_seq@4]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                              |
