|               |                                           HashJoinExec: mode=Partitioned, join_type=Inner, accumulator=MinMaxLeftAccumulator, on=[(ca_county@3, s_county@0), (ca_state@4, s_state@1)], projection=[c_customer_sk@0, ss_sold_date_sk@1, ss_ext_sales_price@2]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                |
